She is losing her mind now, so it might be okay...

74
00:05:48,100 --> 00:05:51,670
No, it won't be okay. Not at all.

75
00:05:51,670 --> 00:05:56,300
Please! I am worried about Grandma.

76
00:05:56,300 --> 00:06:00,670
