77
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:11,670
Pheromone Nomura is absent again.

78
00:06:11,670 --> 00:06:14,070
It sucks!

79
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:19,750
It's meaningless to come to school if I can't smell her.

80
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:22,750
<i>Oh, yeah? Good for you.</i>

81
00:06:22,780 --> 00:06:25,140
<i>I finally received an e-mail from Horikiri-shi a while ago.</i>

82
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:26,810
What did she say?

83
00:06:26,810 --> 00:06:30,050
She only wrote about the workshop.

84
00:06:30,050 --> 00:06:36,460
She said it's been hard but fun. I'm relieved she's doing well.

85
00:06:36,460 --> 00:06:41,020
