116
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:21,970
Could the big guy be...?

117
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:33,200
Okay, I'm going.

118
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:36,550
I'm borrowing this first. I'll give it to you when I'm done.

119
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:38,550
Okay.

120
00:09:41,830 --> 00:09:44,920
He has also been reading it?

121
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:48,870
Did he get inspired, after reading it, to make the figurine, like me?

122
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:24,330
One-inch Princess, come on out.

123
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:27,420
Are you there?

124
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:56,010
There you are!

125
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:01,680
Did you make this for me, Grandma?

126
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:08,870
Well, One-inch Princess should be dressed like that, you know.

127
00:11:09,730 --> 00:11:13,380
I'm so happy. It's beautiful. Thank you so much.

128
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:16,080
I am really happy. <br>(She's using old Japanese.)

129
00:11:19,010 --> 00:11:22,680
Oh? Someone came.

130
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:25,430
<i>It's Mitsuko.</i>

131
00:11:25,430 --> 00:11:27,000
Coming.

132
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,040
- Hide somewhere a bit, okay?<br>- Yup.

133
00:11:34,210 --> 00:11:37,830
I think he doesn't want to see my face.

134
00:11:37,830 --> 00:11:42,700
Why? You used to get along well.

135
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:48,460
Well, I wonder if he hasn't loved me that much from the beginning.

136
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:51,120
He used to love someone very much.

137
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:56,160
Because she broke his heart, he just got together with me who was around him.

138
00:11:58,620 --> 00:12:01,750
Okay, it's ready.

139
00:12:12,330 --> 00:12:13,390
It must be under there.

140
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:16,960
<i>We got two children, and the restaurant business keeps us busy.</i>

141
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:21,290
<i>So, I have been living, not thinking about those things.</i>

142
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:25,870
