144
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:37,540
But, Master has been really in love with you since he married you, hasn't he?

145
00:12:37,540 --> 00:12:44,000
That's not true. Because... I haven't been proposed.

146
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,080
<i>- What?</i><br>- What!?

147
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,290
<i>Oh, is that right?</i>

148
00:12:48,290 --> 00:12:54,290
