168
00:14:16,450 --> 00:14:19,540
all thanks to you, Ricchan.

169
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:21,790
That's not true.

170
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:24,000
You know, Ricchan,

171
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:28,480
