00:16:55,810 --> 00:16:58,730
Hello.

201
00:16:58,730 --> 00:17:02,250
- Oh, hi.<br>- Hello.

202
00:17:02,250 --> 00:17:05,330
- Want some cake?<br>- No, I'll drink something.

203
